Package: mini007
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight Framework for Building Multi-Agents LLM Sequential Orchestration Processes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mohamed El Fodil Ihaddaden
Maintainer: Mohamed El Fodil Ihaddaden <ihaddaden.fodeil@gmail.com>
Description: Provides tools for creating stateful LLM agents using R6 classes and
    the 'ellmer' package. Tracks prompts, messages, and agent metadata for 
    reproducible, multi-turn LLM sessions.
